```{r}
# . At least one hierarchical cluster analysis. Be aware cluster analysis can only be used on numerical variables - dont' use any categorical variables in the cluster analysis.
library(ape)
#Read the data file.
allData17 <- read.csv("NYCHVS 2017 Occupied File for ASA Challenge_CSV.csv", TRUE)
arr_dist <- dist(allData17, method = "euclidean")
arr_clust <- hclust(arr_dist)
arr_tree <- as.phylo(arr_clust)
plot(arr_tree, cex = 0.1)
```
